##DESCRIPTION
##  Cryptography: Common word analysis with an autokey cipher
##ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Cryptography)
## DBchapter(Classic ciphers)
## DBsection(Autokey cipher)
## Date(7/6/2018)
## Institution(University of Southern Mississippi)
